title: See You At The Zeitroads 12/11: FKA Twigs, New Nevada/New California, #FreePS5, Chris Evans
itunes:title: See You At The Zeitroads 12/11: FKA Twigs, New Nevada/New California, #FreePS5, Chris Evans
description:
On this edition of See You At The Zeitroads Miles, Anna, and DJ Danl discuss FKA Twigs coming forward about her abusive relationship with Shia Labeouf, some people want to split off Nevada and California into "New" states, everyone wants a #FreePS5 and are kidding themselves, and Chris Evans is slated to play Buzz Lightyear!
